@startuml comunicacao-UC11
title VetCare+ - Diagrama de Comunicacao UC-11: Pagar Consulta (Pix)

object "Tutor" as Tutor <<actor>>
object "SPA React" as UI
object "PagamentoController" as Ctrl
object "PagamentoService" as Svc
object "PagamentoRepo" as Repo
object "Gateway Pix" as Pix
object "RabbitMQ" as MQ
object "NotificacaoWorker" as Notif

Tutor --> UI : 1: confirmar pagamento Pix
UI --> Ctrl : 2: POST /pagamentos (consultaId, valor)
Ctrl --> Svc : 3: pagar(consultaId, PIX, valor)
Svc --> Repo : 4: criar(Pagamento(PENDENTE))
Repo --> Svc : 4.1: pagamento(id)
Svc --> Pix : 5: gerarCobranca(valor, idempotencyKey)
Pix --> Svc : 5.1: qrCode + txid + expiraEm
Svc --> Repo : 6: atualizar(status=PROCESSANDO, txid)
Svc --> Ctrl : 7: QrCodeDTO
Ctrl --> UI : 8: 200 OK + qrCode
UI --> Tutor : 9: exibir QR Code

Pix --> Ctrl : 10: webhook(txid, APROVADO)
Ctrl --> Svc : 11: confirmar(txid)
Svc --> Repo : 12: atualizar(status=APROVADO, pagoEm)
Svc --> MQ : 13: publicar(PagamentoConfirmadoEvent)
MQ --> Notif : 14: consumir evento
Notif --> Tutor : 15: enviar recibo por e-mail

note bottom
  Fluxo resumido:
  1-9. Tutor inicia cobranca e recebe QR.
  10-12. Gateway confirma via webhook.
  13-15. Sistema publica evento e dispara recibo.
  RN-08: Pix expira em 15 min sem confirmacao.
end note

@enduml
